<p>Even non-work, non-school regularly scheduled events in my life â€” basketball games, volleyball games, bible study â€” were hard to distinguish. It wasnâ€™t enough for me to just put â€œvolleyballâ€ in my calendar. I started writing notes about what the final outcome was, who we were playing, how our team felt. Whatever I could to have that event stick out a little more to me.</p>

